    <text>
    <body>
        <p>Hickman County, Kentucky, farmer. North Carolina native. Father of Amanda Stone, John W. Stone, Martha V. Stone, Mary E. Stone, Margaret F. Stone, Elbert W. Stone, Archibald D. Stone, Ida M. Stone, and Enoch F. Stone. Farmer in Hickman County, Kentucky, in 1860.</p>

